{"tid":1755931,"cid":5,"subCid":12,"title":"投票之後，可以出咩文宣？","createTime":"2019-11-25T23:09:00.000Z","updateTime":"2019-11-25T23:09:23.000Z","uid":332340,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"2f4691029854753c1bfc0b9a3cc7449d6fd08971","tid":1755931,"uid":332340,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-25T23:09:00.000Z","msg":"依家文宣其實係要俾對家睇，所以暫時應該向呢個方向發展。<br />\n<br />\n第一類係投票有穩定社會作用，睇下呢幾日幾平靜，例子：<br />\n- 實行雙普選；才有真安寧<br />\n- 有民主，有安寧；請即推行雙普選<br />\n- 藍黃一齊贏；唯有雙普選<br />\n<br />\n第二類係向警隊，例子：<br />\n- 古有兔死狗烹；今有民死警烹<br />\n- 警隊高層涼冷氣；前線警員吸毒氣<br />\n- 保護妻兒；免被消失；搜集證據；今日開始<br />\n<br />\n因為唔太識做圖，所以先出住文。<br />\n<br />\n暫時係咁先"},{"pid":"fe204a329fc6c2dd69d2e0836e845e3d92217471","tid":1755931,"uid":234961,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-25T23:09:23.000Z","msg":"放錯台係我岸鳩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />求幫推<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/ass.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/ass.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/ass.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />P牌推唔到<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n推上熱門：新戰線&mdash;用建制方法贏建制<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1755527\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1755527</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"}]}